data.description: This conveniently situated condo features two large bedrooms (not the smaller junior suite Palms two bedroom), an open concept living dining area, two full baths, brand new paint on walls, trim, and ceilings, and is one of just two units at this resort to feature three separate decks! This condo features direct views over Destin's largest lagoon pool -complete with waterfall, additional heated pool, huge hot tub, splash pad, on-site restaurant, bar, coffee shop, a large fitness center, ball courts and playground. The resort has three story parking garage, and is conveniently situated less than 1/8 mile to Destin's world famous white sand and emerald water. Second floor, first door from elevator and stairs, sold furnished, and your HOA fee includes electricity, water, trash and internet.
